&lt;p&gt;Urschel, a 100% employee-owned company, is seeking a Risk Engineer to evaluate machine designs for compliance with applicable safety standards and industry regulations, and to develop solutions that minimize or eliminate operator risk. This role provides technical leadership focused on regulatory compliance, hazard identification, risk assessment and cost-effective risk management for Urschel customers. This onsite position reports to the Electrical Engineering Manager and is based at our corporate Headquarters in Chesterton, Indiana.&lt;/p&gt;
